flowchart TD
    A[Visitor arrives at The Tin Website] --> B{What are you here for?}

    B --> C[See What's On]
    B --> D[Hire Rehearsal Space]
    B --> E[Private / Venue Hire]
    B --> F[Support / Fund The Tin]
    B --> G[Live on Stage - LOS]

    C --> C1[Visual event listings]
    C --> C2[Genre & vibe tags]
    C --> C3[Set times & lineup]
    C --> C4[Mobile ticket purchase]

    D --> D1[Rehearsal Rooms page]
    D --> D2[Gear list & pricing]
    D --> D3[Book easily - no emailing]
    D --> D4[See photos of space]

    E --> E1{Type of hire?}
    E1 --> E2[Party / Wedding]
    E1 --> E3[Community / Regular slot]
    E1 --> E4[Promoter / Gig Night]

    E2 --> E2a[Decorated space photos]
    E2 --> E2b[Capacity & layout info]
    E2 --> E2c[Clear hire process]

    E3 --> E3a[Regular slot booking]
    E3 --> E3b[Discounts for regulars]
    E3 --> E3c[Community feel - not corporate]

    E4 --> E4a[Tech spec / PA / stage size]
    E4 --> E4b[Daytime mode photos]
    E4 --> E4c[Clear Promote Enquiries contact]

    F --> F1[About / Impact page]
    F --> F2[Stories of people helped]
    F --> F3[Clear Support / Donate CTA]
    F --> F4[Logo of partners & funders]

    G --> G1{Who are you?}
    G1 --> G2[Parent]
    G1 --> G3[Young Musician]
    G1 --> G4[Industry Scout]

    G2 --> G2a[Safety & safeguarding info]
    G2 --> G2b[Clear ages & structure]
    G2 --> G2c[CTA to join / sign up]

    G3 --> G3a[Dedicated LOS section]
    G3 --> G3b[See other young bands]
    G3 --> G3c[Easy sign-up]

    G4 --> G4a[Roster-style band pages]
    G4 --> G4b[Music links - Spotify etc]
    G4 --> G4c[Performance photos]
    G4 --> G4d[Genre info]
